<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RTI Application</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #008000;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .form-field {
            margin: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .field-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            min-width: 200px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .field-value {
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #000;
            min-height: 20px;
            padding: 2px 5px;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .signature-block {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            width: 200px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-top: 5px;
            padding-top: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .italic {
            font-style: italic;
        }
        .underline {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>APPLICATION UNDER THE RIGHT TO INFORMATION ACT, 2005</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <p>To,</p>
            <p>The Public Information Officer (PIO),</p>
            <p><span class="bold">{{ public_authority | default('[Public Authority Name]') }}</span></p>
            <p>Department: <span class="bold">{{ department | default('[Department Name]') }}</span></p>
            <p>Address: [Public Authority Address]</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Subject: Request for Information under RTI Act, 2005</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Respected Sir/Madam,</p>
            <p>I, <span class="bold">{{ applicant_name | default('[Applicant Name]') }}</span>, son/daughter of [Father's Name], residing at <span class="bold">{{ applicant_address | default('[Applicant Address]') }}</span>, wish to seek the following information under the Right to Information Act, 2005:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Information Sought:</div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>{{ information_sought | default('[Information Sought]') | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Period for which information is sought:</span> {{ period_of_information | default('[Period of Information]') }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I am an Indian citizen and I am seeking this information in my capacity as a citizen.</p>
            <p>I have paid the prescribed fee of INR 10/- (Rupees Ten Only) vide <span class="bold">{{ payment_details | default('[Payment Details]') }}</span>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I assure you that I shall not misuse the information received.</p>
            <p>Kindly provide the information at the earliest.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Thanking you,</p>
            <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <p>(<span class="bold">{{ applicant_name | default('[Applicant Name]') }}</span>)</p>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <p>Date: <span class="bold">{{ date_of_application | default('[Date of Application]') }}</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Note: This is a draft RTI application. Ensure all details are accurate and submit to the relevant Public Information Officer.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
